## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Escopo de Negocio (Regra #5){{else}}Business Scope (Rule #5){{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
Este modulo e dono de **toda logica de negocio** voltada aos frontends.

**RESPONSABILIDADE**: validacoes de dominio, calculos, transformacoes de dados, regras condicionais, agregacoes e metricas, decisoes de workflow, autenticacao/autorizacao.

**FORA DO ESCOPO**:
- Logica de motor/pipeline/scheduler → modulo agent-ai
- Logica de apresentacao/UI → modulos frontend
- DDL/schema → modulo database
{{else}}
This module owns **all business logic** serving the frontends.

**RESPONSIBILITY**: domain validations, calculations, data transformations, conditional rules, aggregations and metrics, workflow decisions, authentication/authorization.

**OUT OF SCOPE**:
- Engine/pipeline/scheduler logic → agent-ai module
- Presentation/UI logic → frontend modules
- DDL/schema → database module
{{/if}}

